{"tid":1467700,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"搵到解決內鬼既方法","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:29:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:49:02.000Z","uid":168969,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"bc5091c414857480c7232e1b0562182c4102f73b","tid":1467700,"uid":168969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:29:35.000Z","msg":"捉到內鬼 冇搞事 冇傷害人既 可以係記者面前邀請佢走<br />\n<br />\n捉到搞事既 可以用適當既武力制服佢 唔洗打佢（我知大家都好嬲）制服完佢 係時候要交個波俾對家拆彈 佢做唔做野 全香港人睇住 記者影底晒 唔做野佢死緊 會觸發更多人不滿<br />\n<br />\n將自己代入執法者既角色 自然拆到內鬼既問題 最重要係得民心<br />\n<br />\n要話俾人知<br />\n佢地控制唔到情緒 我地控制到<br />\n佢地唔做既野 我地做到"},{"pid":"7eecaaa66e8d2209ddabed09cbe4f41e0e58ed0a","tid":1467700,"uid":168969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:32:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dbb78b6359f1e490c37191b046cc18b0a1c09053","tid":1467700,"uid":168969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:33:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7bf28720ab032c9cb63233f75ac78fb6689727c2","tid":1467700,"uid":168969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:35:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b401a53a0bf18fb8252bc1f0c453d8b4e8f84fcd","tid":1467700,"uid":168969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:38:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e74b7c00a99312b670d3a2d519998d7bc4b30963","tid":1467700,"uid":168969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:39:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"204723ac389878e655c3421824a5f50fb973cf45","tid":1467700,"uid":168969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:39:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a1b4091038bd7d1aeb3114031b8c4c0d085ceae2","tid":1467700,"uid":168969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:39:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dfc1b0b44f7a5b5d32d24a8b4dfe7077d96aff67","tid":1467700,"uid":168969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:40:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"547c7563aeab415651e6ac3943068ade235